Class AbstractResultSetTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.jdbc.results.AbstractResultSetTests

  • public abstract class AbstractResultSetTests
extends Object
    Abstract tests for Jena JDBC ResultSet implementations, these tests assume that implementations use the JdbcCompatibility.HIGH compatibility level
